           role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2097-979X")))
Description: Computes dynamic functional connectivity (dynFC) representations
    from BOLD fMRI timeseries. Implements sliding-window Pearson correlation
    (Hansen et al., 2015), edge-centric cofluctuation analysis (Esfahlani
    et al., 2020; Faskowitz et al., 2020), instantaneous phase-locking via
    the Hilbert transform, dynamic phase-locking matrices (dPL), the LEiDA
    leading-eigenvector framework (Cabral et al., 2017; Lord et al., 2019),
    and the Kuramoto order parameter with metastability and Shannon entropy.
    Designed as the upstream dynFC computation layer feeding into stateR for
    brain state metric quantification. Part of the CoDe-Neuro Lab R ecosystem.
